---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
title="Cleaner Standards"
description="Standards expected from cleaners working through CamCleans."
canonicalPath="/cleaner-standards"
>

<section class="hero">
  <div class="container">

    <h1>Cleaner Standards</h1>

    <p class="hero-intro">
      CamCleans works with cleaners who maintain clear professional standards.
      Customers rely on dependable service, respectful conduct and consistent
      cleaning quality across every appointment.
    </p>

  </div>
</section>


<section class="section">
  <div class="container">

    <div class="grid grid-2">

      <div class="card">
        <h2>Reliable Attendance</h2>
        <p>
          Cleaners are expected to arrive at the agreed time and complete the
          scheduled service. Reliability is essential for maintaining trust
          with customers.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h2>Clear Communication</h2>
        <p>
          Communication should remain clear and professional when confirming
          bookings, discussing service requirements or addressing questions.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h2>Professional Behaviour</h2>
        <p>
          Cleaners must maintain respectful conduct while working in customers’
          homes or properties. Professional behaviour is a core expectation of
          the CamCleans network.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h2>Respect for Property</h2>
        <p>
          Customer homes and belongings must be treated with care. Cleaners are
          expected to work responsibly and maintain a professional approach
          throughout the service.
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>

  </div>
</section>


<section class="section section-soft">
  <div class="container">

    <h2>Service Quality Expectations</h2>

    <p class="section-intro">
      Cleaning services arranged through CamCleans should meet consistent
      standards across preparation, cleaning execution and final inspection.
    </p>

    <div class="grid grid-2">

      <div class="card">
        <h3>Consistent Cleaning Standards</h3>
        <p>
          Cleaning tasks should be completed thoroughly and consistently across
          all areas included within the service scope.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h3>Appropriate Equipment</h3>
        <p>
          Cleaners should use suitable cleaning tools and products required to
          complete the service effectively.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h3>Attention to Detail</h3>
        <p>
          Professional cleaning requires attention to surfaces, fixtures and
          commonly missed areas to ensure a complete result.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h3>Clear Service Scope</h3>
        <p>
          Cleaning tasks should be understood in advance so both the customer
          and cleaner have clear expectations of the work being carried out.
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>

  </div>
</section>


<section class="section section-cta">
  <div class="container">

    <h2>Join the CamCleans Network</h2>

    <p>
      Professional cleaners who meet these standards can apply to join the
      CamCleans platform and receive customer cleaning enquiries.
    </p>

    <p>
      <a class="button" href="/join-cleaners">Apply as a Cleaner</a>
    </p>

  </div>
</section>

</Layout>